OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FA new clinical trial is underway which
OL,7,Fhopes to improve how quickly ovarian
OL,8,Fcancer is diagnosed.
OL,10,FUniversity Hospitals Southampton is
OL,11,Fleading the study where researchers
OL,12,Fwill see if a medical tampon can help
OL,13,Fspot the early signs of cancer.
OL,15,FCurrently there is no screening
OL,16,Fprocess for ovarian cancer. Doctors
OL,17,Fmust rely on patients to come forward
OL,18,Fwith symptoms - such as persistent
OL,19,Fbloating, stomach pain, loss of
OL,20,Fappetite and needing to urinate more
OL,21,Foften.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
