FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771941809
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FThe team is currently recruiting
OL,7,Fpatients at University Hospital
OL,8,FSouthampton, but will look to recruit
OL,9,Fpatients from further afield in the
OL,10,Ffuture.
OL,12,FA woman who was previously treated for
OL,13,Fthe disease says the new study is
OL,14,Fpromising and vital in the future of
OL,15,Fwomen's health.
OL,17,FDr Alison Farmer was diagnosed with
OL,18,Fovarian cancer when she was 40 and had
OL,19,Fsurgery to remove her ovaries,
OL,20,Ffollowed by chemotherapy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
