OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771941809
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FDr Alison Farmer, Former ovarian
OL,7,Fcancer patient and Psycho-oncology
OL,8,Fnurse said: "Luckily my cancer was
OL,9,Fcaught early, which is quite unusual.
OL,11,F"There haven't been many advances in
OL,12,Fovarian cancer detection or treatment
OL,13,Fover the years and you know sadly a
OL,14,Fsignificant number of women are still
OL,15,Fdying despite some new drugs so I
OL,16,Fthink anything like this which is a
OL,17,Freasonably easy study to do and take
OL,18,Fpart is really exciting."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
