FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771941809
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FDr Jemma Longley, Consultant Medical
OL,7,FOncologist, University Hospital
OL,8,FSouthampton said: "At the moment the
OL,9,Ffocus of early detectency is on blood-
OL,10,Fbased markers and that puts the onus
OL,11,Fon the patient to go and find a health
OL,12,Fprofessional to do that blood test you
OL,13,Fhave to be registered with a gp
OL,14,Fsurgery you have to make time for that.
OL,16,F"There's a lot of women that are very
OL,17,Fbusy with jobs and children and things
OL,18,Fso I wanted to figure out how we make
OL,19,Fa screening test that could be done in
OL,20,Fyour own home, that was community
OL,21,Fbased and accessible to all .
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
