PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771941809
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,F"This could be a massive gamechanger
OL,7,Ffor women diagnosed with ovarian
OL,8,Fcancer and also other cancers of the
OL,9,Fgynocological tract.
OL,11,F"We could open this up to different
OL,12,Fcancers so cervical cancer,
OL,13,Fendometrial cancers, and potentially
OL,14,Fcreate a multi cancer detection test
OL,15,Fwith the diagnostic tampon."
OL,17,FAccording to NHS Choices, symptoms of
OL,18,Fovarian cancer include:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
