PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771941809
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FDr Victoria Goss, Associate Professor
OL,7,Fof Early Diagnosis, Southampton
OL,8,FClinical Trials Unit said: "Symptoms
OL,9,Fof Ovarian cancer can often crossover
OL,10,Fwith other conditions.
OL,12,F"Therefore it can be really difficult
OL,13,Fto pinpoint the fact that they are
OL,14,Fcancer, so if we have the biomarker of
OL,15,Fthe early stages of cancer that means
OL,16,Fwhen patients are presenting with
OL,17,Fpotentially vague symptoms like some
OL,18,Fabdominal pain and weight loss, these
OL,19,Fbiomarkers can be used to figure out
OL,20,Fif that patient actually does have
OL,21,Fcancer."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
